OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,FThe Bank of Scotland has unveiled a
OL,7,Flimited edition #20 note featuring an
OL,8,Fimage inspired by Scott McTominay's
OL,9,Ffamous overhead kick.
OL,11,FIt has been created to celebrate
OL,12,FScotland's return to the World Cup,
OL,13,Fand fans will have a chance to win one
OL,14,Fof just 100 brand new notes in the
OL,15,Fcoming weeks.
OL,17,FThe design blends traditional banknote
OL,18,Felements with imagery inspired by
OL,19,FMcTominay's World Cup qualifying goal
OL,20,Ffor Scotland against Denmark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
