OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,FThe team sealed their place at the
OL,7,Fmen's international tournament for the
OL,8,Ffirst time since 1998 with a dramatic
OL,9,F4-2 win over Denmark at Hampden Park
OL,10,Fin Glasgow in November.
OL,12,FMcTominay scored the first goal early
OL,13,Fin the game with an overhead kick.
OL,15,FThe midfielder said: "Reaching the
OL,16,Fbiggest stage of world football is
OL,17,Fsomething every player dreams of, and
OL,18,FI know it means everything to our fans.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779678250
OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,F"Moments like that belong to everyone
OL,7,Fwho follows the team, so seeing my
OL,8,Fgoal featured on a Scottish banknote
OL,9,Ffeels incredibly special.
OL,11,F"Being able to work with Bank of
OL,12,FScotland to turn it into something
OL,13,Fthat also supports Crisis, and the
OL,14,Fwork they do to tackle homelessness,
OL,15,Fmakes me even more proud."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
