OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,FEmma Noble, chair of the Scottish
OL,7,Fexecutive committee at the Bank of
OL,8,FScotland, said: "Securing
OL,9,Fqualification in such dramatic fashion
OL,10,Fis a moment fans will never forget,
OL,11,Fand we wanted to mark it in a way
OL,12,Fthat's rooted in Scottish identity.
OL,14,F"Like football, banknotes have long
OL,15,Fbeen part of our country's story, and
OL,16,Fthis limited edition #20 note combines
OL,17,Fthose two traditions with a modern,
OL,18,Fcreative twist.
OL,26,@pD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779678250
OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,F"Scott's overhead kick is already
OL,7,Fregarded as one of the nation's
OL,8,Fgreatest ever goals.
OL,10,F"It's been a privilege to work with
OL,11,Fhim to bring it to life in such a
OL,12,Funique way, and we're grateful for his
OL,13,Fsupport in helping raise funds for
OL,14,FCrisis as they work to end
OL,15,Fhomelessness across Scotland."
OL,17,FJust 100 of the new limited edition
OL,18,Fnotes have been printed, and 50 are up
OL,19,Ffor grabs through a mix of collector
OL,20,Fauctions, a prize draw, and two pop-up
OL,21,F"vaults".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@^O]}D@AOU}D@HO]
