OL,3,CNew #20 banknote to feature Scott
OL,4,CMcTominay's famous overhead kick
OL,6,FAuction and prize draw proceeds will
OL,7,Fsupport Crisis Scotland, the national
OL,8,Fcharity for people experiencing
OL,9,Fhomelessness.
OL,11,FThe online auction is live now and
OL,12,Fruns until 11am on Friday June 26, and
OL,13,Ffans can enter the prize draw until
OL,14,F11am that day.
OL,16,FThe two pop-up vaults will appear in
OL,17,FGlasgow and Edinburgh giving fans the
OL,18,Fchance to crack the code and get their
OL,19,Fhands on one of the limited edition
OL,20,Fnotes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
